* Genika, exei ylopoih8ei olh h ektash tou sygekrimenou zhthmatos.

* Eidikotera, To prwto meros me tis metrikes synarthseis, einai artiws oloklhrwmeno. 

* Sto deytero meros, to Query 1 leitourgei kanonika. Ta ypoloipa, enw einai men grammena oloklhra, 
  parousiazoun orismena provlhmata en merei. Pio sygekrimena,to Query 2 nosei apo ena segmentation fault, to opoio den kataferame mexri 
  kai thn teleytaia stigmh na broume. Parallhla, to Query 4, exei syggrafei eks oloklyrou, alla den 
  exei prolavei na testaristei plhrws.

****GIA NA DIABASEI TO PART 2 APO TA ARXEIA, TA XREIAZETAI SE ENA FAKELO ME ONOMA DataSet ston idio fakelo me to ektelesimo ***
