#############
#	PART 3	#
#############

****GIA NA DIABASEI TO PART 3 APO TA ARXEIA, TA XREIAZETAI SE ENA FAKELO ME ONOMA DataSetPart3 ston idio fakelo me to ektelesimo ***
***PROSOXH: perimenei person.csv kai oxi persons.csv***

* Exei ylopoih8ei o scheduler me skopo thn epiteyksh ths parallhlias ston ypologismo twn top n forums. 
  To prwtokolo pou ylopoiei ton scheduler epiterepei thn pragmatopoihsh parallhlias kai se polles alles
  periptwseis ston kwdika mas, opws gia paradeigma ston filereader. Par' ola ayta kai anagnwrizontas
  tis tromaktikes dynatothtes sth beltiwsh ths apodoshs to synolikou programmatos mas, protimhsame na
  afhsoume sthn akrh th sygekrimenh strathgikh prokeimenou na dwsoume emfash sthn artioterh syggrafh
  tou synolou ths ergasias.

* Analytikotera, o scheduler leitourgei ws ekshs:
  Dhmiourgountai threads, me to main apo ayta na paragei tasks me sygekrimeno typo to ka8ena, opws forumFill,
  forumCalculation, ktl. Topo8etei, me me8odous sygxronismou mutex kai condition variables opoiodhpote task
  einai epi8ymhto apo emas se mia oura, kataskeyasmenh gia ayto to skopo, thn jobQueue.
  Ta worker threads, synagwnizontai gia thn prosvash sthn oura kai lamvanoun ena task th fora. Analoga me ton
  typo tou, to ekastote task anagnwrizei poia synarthsh prepei na kalesei gia na xeiristei th douleia.

* Oi koines domes pou xrhsimopoei to main kai ta worker threads briskontai se mia global metablhth me onoma globalUtilities. 
  Se ayth yparxoun oloi oi grafoi kai oi koines domes pou prokyptoun mesw toy data set. Ka8e mia domh 
  prostateyetai apo ena mutex. Sto globalUtilities symperilamvanontai epishs kai alles xrhsimes domes,
  opws to jobQueue kai ta topNForums.

* Epipros8etws, exei ylopoih8ei ena extra thread, to opoio exei th dynatothta na termatisei to programma ana
  pasa stigmh kai na doulepsei ws garbage collector, apeley8eronontas, etsi, th mnhmh. 

* Exoun ylopoih8ei kai oi dyo algoritmoi tou 3ou merous, me ton prwto na xrhsimopoiei anadromh gia ton ypologismo
  twn klikwn kai na einai idiaitera grhgoros kai to deytero na einai pio argos alla kai na leitourgei me 
  kapoia memory bugs.




#########################
#	ANAGNWSH ARXEIWN	#
#########################


* Prin ksekinhsei h 'pragmatikh' ektelesh tou programmatos, einai aparaithto na diabastoun ta katallhla arxeia.
  Ka8e ypoprovlhma, apaitei ena yposynolo tou synolikou ari8mou arxeiwn tou Data Set gia na leitourghsei.
  Prin loipwn ton 'xrhsimo' kwdika, exei topo8eth8ei o filereader, h synarthsh pou einai ypey8ynh gia thn
  anagnwsh olou tou Data Set, an ayto einai aparaithto. 

* Kata thn ekkinhsh tou ektelesimou, o xrhsths erwtatai gia ta arxeia person.csv, post.csv, forum.csv, comment.csv
  organisation.csv kai tag.csv, an epi8ymei na diavastoun. H katafatikh apanthsh dhmiourgei ksexwristo grafo
  gia tis adistoixes kathgories. Sth synexeia, ginontai erwthseis gia thn pros8hkh akmwn, opws aytes
  prokyptoun apo to do8en Data Set, gia paradeigma person_knows_person, post_hasCreator_person, ktl.

* Yparxei epishs h dynatothta eisagwghs symmetrikwn akmwn gia dieykolynsh programmatismoy. Gia paradeigma
  h sxesh post_hasCreator_person na symplhrw8ei me thn person_HasCreated_post. 
